                <h1>Criminal Background Check in Michigan: Your Essential Guide</h1>
                <p>In Michigan, a criminal background check can be conducted through the Michigan State Police (MSP) or online via the IChat system. These checks are vital for employment, volunteer work, and gun purchases. Individuals can request their own records or those of others, with varying fees depending on the method used.</p>
